but I'm ready now.

741
00:52:41.040 --> 00:52:43.040
Oh, God.

742
00:52:45.250 --> 00:52:48.550
I knew
you would do this! I knew it!

743
00:52:48.720 --> 00:52:51.720
- Carrie, I'm sorry.
- I am humiliated!

744
00:52:51.890 --> 00:52:54.470
