795
00:57:11.770 --> 00:57:14.770
Jerrod. Smith Jerrod, with a J.

796
00:57:14.940 --> 00:57:18.820
That's right. Great, thank you.

797
00:57:20.150 --> 00:57:24.110
- Make sure that the car is there...
- We're here, I'll call you back later.

798
00:57:27.160 --> 00:57:28.200
Welcome to Mexico.

799
00:57:33.830 --> 00:57:35.420
Do you have wi-fi? Thanks.

800
00:57:39.170 --> 00:57:42.380
I'm sorry, I'm confused.
I'm waiting for a Mr. And Mrs. Preston.

801
00:57:42.550 --> 00:57:46.720
Honey, you'll be waiting a long time.
We'll talk.

802
00:57:53.190 --> 00:57:56.060
This will kill her.

803
00:57:58.020 --> 00:58:00.070
- Where is she?
- In the powder room.

804
00:58:00.230 --> 00:58:02.990
- Well, let's look around.
- Yeah.

805
00:58:33.250 --> 00:58:35.760
And this is a master suite.

806
00:58:37.130 --> 00:58:39.090
Oh, my God.

807
00:58:39.760 --> 00:58:41.430
Here.

808
00:58:41.600 --> 00:58:43.430
You get that side.

809
00:58:45.270 --> 00:58:47.430
